# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
# MANUFACTURING ANALYTICS - STEP 4
# ML PREDICTION MODEL
#
# Is step mein sikhenge:
#   1. Machine Learning kya hota hai - simple explanation
#   2. Data prepare karna (features + labels)
#   3. Train/Test split karna
#   4. Random Forest model banana aur train karna
#   5. Model accuracy check karna
#   6. Naye data pe prediction karna
#   7. Feature importance - kaun sa factor sabse important
#   8. Model save karna (reuse ke liye)
